|ID|OPERATOR              |NAME     |EST. ROWS|COST|
----------------------------------------------------
|0 |NESTED-LOOP CONNECT BY|         |0        |39  |
|1 | TABLE SCAN           |siblingst|1        |38  |
|2 | TABLE SCAN           |siblingst|5        |37  |
====================================================

